KSL.com’s new Uplifting Utah column showcases the good done by those around you.
“Not knowing what they could do about it, they explained, 'I called in to WVCPD non-emergency and got to speak with Officer Christiansen.
But shortly after the call, Officer Christiansen came in and picked up their order (and would not let us donate it for free.)
Thank you, Officer Christiansen for showing how we do it in WVC!"
